(10, 1, '2012-05-12 20:49:42', '2012-05-13 00:49:42', '<p>Please find links to the necessary information you would need to become a prospective student of Ragamalika. If you have already been learning Classical music for some time now please let us know what you have learnt till date and From who?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The process of learning carnatic music can be divided into 3 parts</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Beginner- One who has to start from the basic lessons.</li>\r\n	<li>Intermediate- you have already learnt sarali Varisai,Janta varisai,Upper sthyai varisai alankaras, And geetams.</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced- Kritis,Keertanams,Ragam,neraval swar a Kalpanai and more.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Every new student is evaluated individually and then placed in an appropriate group.</p>', 'New Student Info', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'new-student-info', '', '', '2012-08-30 22:25:18', '2012-08-31 02:25:18', '', 0, 'http://bramkaslp01/ragamalika/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
