(370, 1, '2012-08-04 18:09:25', '2012-08-04 22:09:25', 'Please find links to the necessary information you would need to become a prospective student of Ragamalika. If you have already been learning Classical music for some time now please let us know what you have learnt till date and From who?\n\nThe process of learning carnatic music can be divided into 3 parts\n<ul>\n	<li>Beginner- One who has to start from the basic lessons.</li>\n	<li>Intermediate- you have already learnt sarali Varisai,Janta varisai,Upper sthyai varisai alankaras, And geetams.</li>\n	<li>Advanced- Kritis,Keertanams,Ragam,neraval swar a Kalpanai and more.</li>\n</ul>\nEvery new student is evaluated individually and then placed in an appropriate group by <span class="signature">Mrs. Maragatham</span>.', 'New Student Info', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-autosave', '', '', '2012-08-04 18:09:25', '2012-08-04 22:09:25', '', 10, 'http://bramkaslp01/ragamalika/10-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
